: 24px;\" width=\"245\">&gt;=200K小时</td></tr><tr><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">网管功能</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\">支持Console/AUX Modem/Telnet/SSH2.0 命令行配置 支持FTP、TFTP、Xmodem、SFTP文件上下载管理 支持SNMP V1/V2c/V3 支持Netconf 支持RMON 支持NTP时钟 支持故障后报警和自恢复 支持系统工作日志 支持流量分析 支持自动化配置</td><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">Qos支持</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\">支持802.1p 支持SP、WRR、DRR、SP+WRR、SP+DRR等队列调度机制 支持RED/WRED 支持基于出端口/入端口的限速 支持HQoS</td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"paramtable-a\" width=\"765\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><th style=\"width: 104px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(10, 80, 161); text-align: left; padding: 10px 15px 12px; line-height: 26px; white-space: nowrap;\">端口参数</th><td style=\"padding: 12px 0px 6px;\" width=\"629\"><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"paramtable-b\" width=\"765\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">端口类型</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\">576个100GE、288个40GE、1152个25GE、1152个10GE线速端口</td><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">模块插槽数</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\">模块插槽：10个(其中2个用于管理引擎模块) 交换网板槽位：6个</td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"paramtable-a\" width=\"765\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><th style=\"width: 104px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(10, 80, 161); text-align: left; padding: 10px 15px 12px; line-height: 26px; white-space: nowrap;\">电气参数</th><td style=\"padding: 12px 0px 6px;\" width=\"629\"><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"paramtable-b\" width=\"765\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">电压(V)</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\">RG-PA2700I: 100-120Vac 200-240Vac</td><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">功率(W)</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\">RG-PA2700I: 1350W/2700W</td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"paramtable-a\" width=\"765\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><th style=\"width: 104px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(10, 80, 161); text-align: left; padding: 10px 15px 12px; line-height: 26px; white-space: nowrap;\">外观参数</th><td style=\"padding: 12px 0px 6px;\" width=\"629\"><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"paramtable-b\" width=\"765\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">产品尺寸</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\">442×1017×534mm(12U)</td><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\"><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"paramtable-a\" width=\"765\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><th style=\"width: 104px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体; font-size: 22px; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(10, 80, 161); text-align: left; padding: 10px 15px 12px; line-height: 26px; white-space: nowrap;\">环境参数</th><td style=\"padding: 12px 0px 6px;\" width=\"629\"><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"paramtable-b\" width=\"765\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">工作温度(℃)</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\">0℃ 到45℃</td><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">工作湿度</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\">10%到90%RH(无冷凝)</td></tr><tr><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">存储温度(℃)</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\">-40℃到70℃</td><th style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-weight: normal; width: 110px; height: 34px; background: rgb(229, 241, 255); color: rgb(83, 110, 142); text-align: right;\">存储湿度</th><td style=\"border-color: rgb(205, 227, 253); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-right: 6px; line-height: 24px;\" width=\"245\">5%到95%RH</td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 80, 80); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">在淘宝可以购买！<a href=\"https://www.taobao.com/\" target=\"_self\">点击跳转</a>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">如需在线购买的话。请留言，我们会稍后联系你，敬请等候<img src=\"http://img.baidu.com/hi/jx2/j_0076.gif\"/></p><p><br/></p>');
INSERT INTO `yun_product` VALUES ('28', '3', 'CRM(客户关系管理）', '../upload/product/up_5c18b94849a22.jpg', '<p><img src=\"/yiyun/upload/ueditor_img/20181218/1545124099134990.jpg\" title=\"1545124099134990.jpg\"/></p><h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(4, 120, 212);\">CRM(客户关系管理）</h1><p style=\"width: 508px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden;\">多迪CRM客户关系管理系统，适用于服务业、制造业是业内最好用的行业CRM、可跟ERP、OA系统紧密关联，根据客户特性定制，100%实施成功！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><strong>多迪CRM客户关系管理系统</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><strong>最好用的行业ERP</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1/yiyun/upload/ueditor_img/20181218/1545124099102553.jpg\" title=\"1545124099102553.jpg\"/></strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;多迪CRM（客户关系管理系统）在成熟的CRM系统基础上，结合企业行业特性，基于BPM平台打造，是业内最好的行业CRM之一。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;多迪CRM主要包括：市场管理、商机管理、销售管理、客户管理、服务管理、业务员管理、日常管理、报表管理；支持公海、私海应用、项目型客户管理等。</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>多迪CRM特点：</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>&nbsp; 1、产品成熟、稳定、操作简单</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>&nbsp; 2、 根据客户特色开发</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>&nbsp; 3、100%成功上线</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>&nbsp; 4、无线集成了ERP、OA、HR系统</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>多迪CRM主要应用客户：</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;中旭企业管理股份有限公司、 三为管理顾问公司、景阳科技股份、振化富集团</strong></p>');
INSERT INTO `yun_product` VALUES ('29', '3', '智能会议管理系统', '../upload/product/up_5c18be4b58c52.jpg', '<h3 class=\"h3_01\" style=\"padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 30px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; width: 780px; height: 30px; color: rgb(51, 134, 197); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(163, 163, 163); float: left; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">产品概述</h3><p><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; word-break: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; word-break: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; word-break: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; word-break: normal;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">智能会议管理系统既可用于召开党组会、办公会等各类专项会议，也可用于召开部门会议及专题会议，适用于对会议系统通用性要求较高的机关及企事业单位。</span><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; mar