; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; word-break: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; word-break: normal;\">包括会议安排、会议讨论、会议查询等功能。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; word-break: normal; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 class=\"h3_01\" style=\"padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 30px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; width: 780px; height: 30px; color: rgb(51, 134, 197); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(163, 163, 163); float: left; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">产品特点</h3><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><br/></p></li><li><p>可用来召开多类会议，同时方便对个人参加会议的集中管理</p></li><li><p>多点触控的操作方式能大幅提升用户体验</p></li><li><p>采用“会议”的管理模式，便于会议安排和议题管理</p></li><li><p>通过网络共享参会人员屏幕，减少运维成本<br/>&nbsp;</p></li></ul><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; word-break: normal; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 class=\"h3_01\" style=\"padding: